card_text: A positive outcome or advantage gained from something is called a _______. People often seek a _______ when they participate in activities or make decisions. For example, exercising regularly has the _______ of improving health. Companies may offer _______s to employees, such as health insurance or paid time off. In general, a _______ is something that improves your situation or well-being.

The overall setting should convey a sense of well-being and improved quality of life. No text in the image.
